  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prickle is a grid-based, Sokoban-style puzzle game with a laid-back, wholesome vibe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/2f0c0eaa8b0aa55ffe234558791dc184.poster.avif?t=1749323351\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/2f0c0eaa8b0aa55ffe234558791dc184.webm?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/2f0c0eaa8b0aa55ffe234558791dc184.mp4?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your hoglets, scattered throughout the levels, stick to DadHog and to each other, forming a Tetris-like shape - a Prickle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/e998aec4f51d65bf88ec37d65bd3ad94.poster.avif?t=1749323351\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/e998aec4f51d65bf88ec37d65bd3ad94.webm?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/e998aec4f51d65bf88ec37d65bd3ad94.mp4?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need to collect all the hoglets and bring the Prickle back home. However, the more hoglets you collect, the larger and harder it is to squeeze through the narrow spaces in the hedge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/9fdc90f8486706f2744ab918fbe90d3a.poster.avif?t=1749323351\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/9fdc90f8486706f2744ab918fbe90d3a.webm?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/9fdc90f8486706f2744ab918fbe90d3a.mp4?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the right way to collect the hoglets, form your Prickle, and navigate it through the levels to reach home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/b4ea7eec4f87a5843cf25008cb8a062e.poster.avif?t=1749323351\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/b4ea7eec4f87a5843cf25008cb8a062e.webm?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/b4ea7eec4f87a5843cf25008cb8a062e.mp4?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prickle features over 40 levels across 4 seasons, each presenting different challenges and unique mechanics.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prickle is a grid-based, Sokoban-style puzzle game with a laid-back, wholesome vibe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/2f0c0eaa8b0aa55ffe234558791dc184.poster.avif?t=1749323351\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/2f0c0eaa8b0aa55ffe234558791dc184.webm?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/2f0c0eaa8b0aa55ffe234558791dc184.mp4?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your hoglets, scattered throughout the levels, stick to DadHog and to each other, forming a Tetris-like shape - a Prickle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/e998aec4f51d65bf88ec37d65bd3ad94.poster.avif?t=1749323351\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/e998aec4f51d65bf88ec37d65bd3ad94.webm?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/e998aec4f51d65bf88ec37d65bd3ad94.mp4?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need to collect all the hoglets and bring the Prickle back home. However, the more hoglets you collect, the larger and harder it is to squeeze through the narrow spaces in the hedge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/9fdc90f8486706f2744ab918fbe90d3a.poster.avif?t=1749323351\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/9fdc90f8486706f2744ab918fbe90d3a.webm?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/9fdc90f8486706f2744ab918fbe90d3a.mp4?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the right way to collect the hoglets, form your Prickle, and navigate it through the levels to reach home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/b4ea7eec4f87a5843cf25008cb8a062e.poster.avif?t=1749323351\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/b4ea7eec4f87a5843cf25008cb8a062e.webm?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759760/extras/b4ea7eec4f87a5843cf25008cb8a062e.mp4?t=1749323351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prickle features over 40 levels across 4 seasons, each presenting different challenges and unique mechanics.</p>",
